Class BeadledomResteasyClientBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.ws.rs.client.ClientBuilder
      • com.cerner.beadledom.client.BeadledomClientBuilder
        • com.cerner.beadledom.client.resteasy.BeadledomResteasyClientBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.core.Configurable<javax.ws.rs.client.ClientBuilder>

    public class BeadledomResteasyClientBuilder
extends BeadledomClientBuilder
    Abstraction for creating Clients.

    Delegates to ResteasyClientBuilder and additionally adds a default implementation of CorrelationIdFilter.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    John Leacox, Sundeep Paruvu
